<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12400] Fix refguide so it does connection#getTable rather than new HTable everywhere: first cut!</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12400</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The refguide has bits of code in it.  The code does &apos;new HTable&apos; to get a table instance.  Rather, it should be promoting the new style where we get a Connection and then do a getTable on it.  Ditto for references to &apos;new HBaseAdmin&apos;.  See ConnectionFactory for new style.  See also package-info.java in Client for updated example.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Misty, if you are game for this one, I can help w/ how it should look.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
